results.name: A141498(n)/A027760(n).
maple: A141498 := proc(n) A010696(n-1)* A086892(n) ; end: A027760 := proc(n) local s, p; s := 0 ; p := 2; while p <= n+1 do if n mod (p-1) = 0 then s := s+1/p; fi; p := nextprime(p) ; od: denom(s) ; end:
